---
description: Defining time durations, intervals, etc.
alwaysApply: false
---

Use date-fns helpers to specify time durations and intervals.

```ts
// BAD
setInterval(() => {
  /* ... */
}, 1000)

import { secondsToMilliseconds } from 'date-fns'

// GOOD
setInterval(() => {
  /* ... */
}, secondsToMilliseconds(1))
```
